Naming
======

<PRJ><PKT>_METH()

xyzbytearray_fload()
xyzbits_sendto()

    or

<PRJ>_<PKT>_METH()

xyz_bytearray_loadfromfile()
xyz_bits_sendto()

Also is possible standard C (verbal) kind:

xyz_floadbytearray() or xyz_fload_bytearray()
xyz_sendbitsto() or xyz_send_bits_to()

Modules
=======

<PRJ>_<MODULE>

Packages should be in sub-folders.

Standard modules
================

'types.h' - ALL typedefs.
'globals.h' - all global variables (or in it's modules)
'errors.h' - all errors codes, code->str...
'config.h' - general (global) application compile-time config
